vest in government-backed assets from Dh1,000]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131855039.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[UAE residents can now invest in government-backed Islamic Treasury Sukuk with a minimum of Dh1,000, thanks to the launch of the Sovereign Retail T-Sukuk programme. This Shariah-compliant product, developed with the Central Bank, aims to boost savings and financial inclusion by offering individuals direct access to sovereign investment opportunities previously reserved for institutions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-launches-first-retail-t-sukuk-letting-residents-invest-in-government-backed-assets-from-dh1000/articleshow/131855039.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/uae-launches-first-retail-t-sukuk-letting-residents-invest-in-government-backed-assets-from-dh1000/articleshow/131855039.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-19T15:17:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131855114,imgsize-421938.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Last ride': Air Force One Boeing 747 retires after Trump’s France trip, ending 35-year presidential service era]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131854995.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The iconic Boeing 747-200B, a 35-year veteran of presidential service, completed its final flight as Air Force One, carrying President Trump back from France. This long-serving aircraft, affectionately nicknamed 'SAM 2900', is being retired. A newly refitted Boeing 747, gifted by Qatar, is set to take over presidential duties, with a potential inaugural flight to Mount Rushmore next month.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/last-ride-air-force-one-boeing-747-retires-after-trumps-france-trip-ending-35-year-presidential-service-era/articleshow/131854995.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/last-ride-air-force-one-boeing-747-retires-after-trumps-france-trip-ending-35-year-presidential-service-era/articleshow/131854995.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-19T15:10:59+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131855047,imgsize-63699.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[UK information commissioner John Edwards quits after workplace probe over ‘inappropriate humour’ ]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131857999.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/inappropriate-humour-poor-judgement-uk-information-commissioner-john-edwards-quits-after-workplace-probe/articleshow/131857999.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/inappropriate-humour-poor-judgement-uk-information-commissioner-john-edwards-quits-after-workplace-probe/articleshow/131857999.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-19T17:17:07+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131858338,imgsize-57872.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Man arrested after 3-year-old boy found injured in Cambridgeshire zoo crocodile enclosure]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131853683.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A three-year-old boy is in critical condition after being found inside a crocodile enclosure at a Cambridgeshire zoo. A 30-year-old man was arrested on suspicion of attempted murder. Zoo staff are credited with a swift rescue. Police are investigating the incident and have urged the public not to speculate.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/man-arrested-after-3-year-old-boy-found-injured-in-cambridgeshire-zoo-crocodile-enclosure/articleshow/131853683.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/man-arrested-after-3-year-old-boy-found-injured-in-cambridgeshire-zoo-crocodile-enclosure/articleshow/131853683.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-19T14:15:27+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131853736,imgsize-1084792.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Andy Burnham wins crucial Makerfield by-election, intensifying pressure on PM Keir Starmer]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131851702.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Andy Burnham's decisive Makerfield by-election victory has intensified pressure on Labour leader Sir Keir Starmer. Winning nearly 55% of the vote, Burnham's return to Westminster signals a potential challenge to Starmer's leadership and Labour's future direction. The result is seen as a significant moment, fueling debate about the party's strategy and its ability to reconnect with voters.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/andy-burnham-wins-crucial-makerfield-by-election-intensifying-pressure-on-pm-keir-starmer/articleshow/131851702.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/andy-burnham-wins-crucial-makerfield-by-election-intensifying-pressure-on-pm-keir-starmer/articleshow/131851702.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-19T13:48:39+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1